fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 gained 35.20 points or 0.19% to settle at 18,633.85. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, fell 2.33% to 12.01. HDFC Bank, Apollo Hospitals Enterprise and Kotak Mahindra Bank were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The June 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 29 June 2023.
